## 📝 Description

💡 This project leverages **Node.js** and **PostgreSQL** to store and manipulate information about employees. It keeps track of details such as:

- Salaries
- Positions
- Department roles
- Hierarchical structures (e.g., who reports to whom)

✨ The application is designed to make employee data management efficient and straightforward!

